By: Thomas Traherne
---
You never know yourself till you know more than your body. The Image of
God was not seated in the features of your face, but in the lineaments of
your Soul. In the knowledge of your Powers, Inclinations, and Principles,
the knowledge of yourself chiefly consisteth.
